cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.MED, cs.CL 

The paper deals with developing an algorithm for detecting pneumonia from chest X-rays using deep learning techniques. This falls under the domain of computer vision (cs.CV) and machine learning (cs.LG, cs.AI). Additionally, the paper deals with medical imaging and healthcare applications, which could also place it under the categories of medical imaging (cs.MED) and natural language processing (cs.CL) for analyzing radiologist annotations.
